    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model demonstrates acceptable predictive performance for hemolysis-relevant QoIs with reasonable fidelity to experimental reference data. The Requirement is judged to be satisfied based on the credibility team's evaluation of simulation quality against established cardiovascular CFD best practices. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met at all five operating points. The package is accepted for regulatory submission supporting the Class II CPB device 510(k) submission.",
